    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to aluminum honeycomb-core solid support panels. These may be used in various capacities including as an auxiliary support for paintings on fabric in the conservation field: they supply an alternative to bonding to another piece of fabric as method of consolidation.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
